{"tid":1950740,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"深水埗郵局對面果間連鎖黃店個老闆同我入黎，唔該你再培訓下你啲員工。","createTime":"2020-03-30T13:36:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T13:46:39.000Z","uid":69334,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"853267c4ade18a0f3ea5e4c91be29c8ba1de17ed","tid":1950740,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T13:36:08.000Z","msg":"頭先開錯台，依家開番喺吹水區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n限坐令下，你要食客搭枱我都唔太介意，因為都想你地有多啲生意做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搭緊枱果陣坐對面果條友邊食野，邊大聲講電話講左成個字，同你啲員工反映，只係想你啲員工幫手叫果條友收線或者出去講，你啲員工屌鳩我話無得換位？好彩你另外有員工知衰，幫屌我個呀姐補鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有探熱係每個食客都要做，你自己睇下cctv你啲員工有無做足啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔該老細你攪攪佢，大家都想黃色經濟圈壯大。提就提左，下次唔好彩係便衣狗入黎放蛇就唔怨點解會比人捉，正常藍既果下已經會即call狗黎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd486fa7023958ed6d27635015cb60bcdb34ab1d","tid":1950740,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T13:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d7d7410665b43cd194f0dce79131966c8a4ed7","tid":1950740,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T13:45:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07d30da0f44ddafbb6cd53776d6ef041bce99b69","tid":1950740,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T13:46:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}